article_id:1268,category_name:News,title_name:The First Round of Limited-Time Packs Are Here!,image_path:https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/0cd237bc1ea64c0812fc62d5579d28f6.png,message:<div>Limited-time packs are available under Limited-Time Deals in the Shop as of <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1588226400"></span>!</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/36acd435adbf2d20c71b07826abd2629.png"></div><div>■Availability Period</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1588226400"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1589263140"></span></div><div><br></div><div>■Limited-Time Adventurer Upgrade Pack</div><div>This pack contains diamantium, 10 champion&#39;s testaments, and more.</div><div><br></div><div>&lt;Diamantium Included&gt;</div><div>・Diamantium x 4,800 (3,920 Diamantium + 880 Bonus)</div><div><br></div><div>&lt;Other Items Included&gt;</div><div>・Champion&#39;s Testament x10</div><div>・Knight&#39;s Testament x10</div><div>・Gold Crystal x1,000</div><div>・Mana x1,000,000</div><div><br></div><div>■Limited-Time 5★ Dragon Upgrade Special</div><div>This pack contains diamantium, a voucher to summon a 5★ dragon, and items useful for upgrading dragons.</div><div><br></div><div>&lt;Diamantium Included&gt;</div><div>・Diamantium x1,500 (1,200 + 300 bonus)</div><div><br></div><div>&lt;Other Items Included&gt;</div><div>・5★ Summon Voucher (Dragon) x1</div><div>・Succulent Dragonfruit x30</div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>・When you have a 5★ Summon Voucher (Dragon), you can perform a 5★ Dragon Summon from the main Summon page.</div><div>・In a 5★ Dragon Summon, you use a 5★ Summon Voucher (Dragon) and will be guaranteed to summon one 5★ dragon.</div><div>・To check appearance rates for the 5★ Dragon Summon, open the Shop from the Home page, then select Limited-Time Deals, pick the Limited-Time 5★ Dragon Upgrade Special, and select 5★ Dragon Appearance Rates in the pop-up that appears after tapping Purchase.</div><div><br></div><div>■Limited-Time Flame Unbind Special</div><div>This pack contains diamantium and items to assist with unlocking the mana nodes of flame-attuned adventurers.</div><div><br></div><div>&lt;Diamantium Included&gt;</div><div>・Diamantium x700 (480 + 220 bonus)</div><div><br></div><div>&lt;Other Items Included&gt;</div><div>・Incandescence Orb x50</div><div>・Inferno Orb x10</div><div>・Blaze Orb x30</div><div>・Flame Orb x120</div><div>・Flamewyrm&#39;s Scaldscale x40</div><div>・Flamewyrm&#39;s Scale x70</div><div>・Rainbow Orb x10</div><div>・Champion&#39;s Testament x1</div><div><br></div><div>Note:</div><div>・This product is not available in some countries/regions.</div><div><br></div><div>■Limited-Time Light Unbind Special</div><div>This pack contains diamantium and items to assist with unlocking the mana nodes of light-attuned adventurers.</div><div><br></div><div>&lt;Diamantium Included&gt;</div><div>・Diamantium x700 (480 + 220 bonus)</div><div><br></div><div>&lt;Other Items Included&gt;</div><div>・Resplendence Orb x50</div><div>・Refulgence Orb x10</div><div>・Radiance Orb x30</div><div>・Light Orb x120</div><div>・Lightwyrm&#39;s Glowscale x40</div><div>・Lightwyrm&#39;s Scale x70</div><div>・Rainbow Orb x10</div><div>・Champion&#39;s Testament x1</div><div><br></div><div>Note:</div><div>・This product is not available in some countries/regions.</div><div><br></div><div>■Limited-Time Shadow Unbind Special</div><div>This pack contains diamantium and items to assist with unlocking the mana nodes of shadow-attuned adventurers.</div><div><br></div><div>&lt;Diamantium Included&gt;</div><div>・Diamantium x700 (480 + 220 bonus)</div><div><br></div><div>&lt;Other Items Included&gt;</div><div>・Abaddon Orb x50</div><div>・Nether Orb x10</div><div>・Nightfall Orb x30</div><div>・Shadow Orb x120</div><div>・Shadowwyrm&#39;s Darkscale x40</div><div>・Shadowwyrm&#39;s Scale x70</div><div>・Rainbow Orb x10</div><div>・Champion&#39;s Testament x1</div><div><br></div><div>Note:</div><div>・This product is not available in some countries/regions.</div><div><br></div><div>■Limited-Time Champion&#39;s Pack</div><div>This pack contains diamantium and items useful for upgrading adventurers and assist with unlocking mana nodes.</div><div><br></div><div>&lt;Diamantium Included&gt;</div><div>・Diamantium x300 (192 + 108 bonus)</div><div><br></div><div>&lt;Other Items Included&gt;</div><div>・Gold Crystal x300</div><div>・Champion&#39;s Testament x1</div><div>・Mana x75,000</div><div><br></div><div>Note:</div><div>・This product is not available in some countries/regions.</div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. Check Appearance Rates on the pack purchase screen to see the lineup of dragons available using the 5★ Summon Voucher (Dragon).</div><div>2. For information about each pack, select the Shop on the Home page, and see Limited-Time Deals.</div><div>3. Each limited-time pack may only be purchased once during the availability period.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1588226400,update_time1588037669